response: A trip to Leh and Ladakh sounds nice for you. You can go for rafting, long drives across dangerous valleys of the Himalayas , mountain climbing, monasteries, and much more. The most famous tourist package out there is the Leh-Nubra-Pangong Triangle tour, you can hire a car+driver or go biking across some of the most challenging roads of the world and will be able to experience breath taking landscapes each one being a potential award winning landscape photograph throughout your trip.Do you want to explore more?
